{"tid":603924,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"入嚟講下那些年你錯過咗嘅男仔/女仔","createTime":"2018-03-24T08:10:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-24T14:00:54.000Z","uid":21220,"like":6,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ad3c1ed4129e267647ea97cb8a3cd591f83e5835","tid":603924,"uid":21220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T08:10:26.000Z","msg":"讀同一間中學同一級 <br />\n本來同你唔係好熟甚至唔識咁濟<br />\n到中六嘅時候大家一齊奮戰DSE<br />\n因為我數學好你成日都會過嚟問我數<br />\n其實feel到你對我有好感<br />\n但係我當時仲未放低哂上一任 所以成日避開你<br />\n畢業後大家各行各路冇聯絡過 差唔多四年冇見<br />\n直到尋日撞到你一齊返工返學<br />\n我就嚟大學畢業仲未知自己想做咩<br />\n而你已經出咗嚟做野兩年有哂目標知道自己想點<br />\n地鐡分開轉線之後噤電話先醒起連你電話號碼都冇<br />\n見你而家生活得咁好 想同你講 祝福你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申ff 第一次開post有咩錯嘅各位巴絲屌得細力啲"},{"pid":"f38732d971a0c9aec64e823a10c2b29d4a2171b0","tid":603924,"uid":21220,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T08:13:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdf987f04a3f8ce11c735c8222f9716e15b2fcee","tid":603924,"uid":21220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T08:43:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推</span></span>"},{"pid":"0ac363ca7d2c83a999b824f9656332773a6067e2","tid":603924,"uid":125553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T08:47:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a84ab495811fb6233040ae82c9c58898adac83","tid":603924,"uid":154871,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T10:31:05.000Z","msg":"唔熟 想搵佢又驚佢覺得煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d428ac8db0d7b28077ca35a7713f270b39506f80","tid":603924,"uid":60787,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T10:36:53.000Z","msg":"啱啱我就錯過咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多嘢都好夾，但係我本身A0，唔識點追女仔，嚇親佢